    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDef_2">Definitions:\n
• Bound of Absolute Error (Sum/Diff): h_(a±b) = h_a + h_b.\n
• Bound of Relative Error:\n
ε_(a+b) = (h_a + h_b)/(a + b), ε_(a-b) = (h_a + h_b)/|a - b|.\n
• Subtraction of similar numbers increases relative error.</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDefQuestion_2">If h_a = 0.1 and h_b = 0.2, what is the bound of absolute error of a + b?</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDefAnswerOne_2">0.1</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDefAnswerTwo_2">0.2</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDefAnswerThree_2">0.3</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryDefCorrectAnswer_2">0.3</string>

    <string name="SectionFourTheoryProperties_2">Properties:\n
Practical Rule for Add/Subtract:\n
1. Find the least accurate term.\n
2. Round others to one more decimal.\n
3. Compute result.\n
4. Round result to same accuracy as the least precise term.</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryPropsQuestion_2">Which operation between nearly equal numbers causes the relative error to increase sharply?</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryPropsAnswerOne_2">Addition</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryPropsAnswerTwo_2">Subtraction</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryPropsAnswerThree_2">Multiplication</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryPropsCorrectAnswer_2">Subtraction</string>

    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExamples_2">Add 12.3 (h = 0.05) and 4.56 (h = 0.005).\n
Step 1: Least accurate term: 12.3 (1 decimal place).\n
Step 2: Round 4.56 to one extra decimal: 4.56 → keep as 4.56.\n
Step 3: Sum = 12.3 + 4.56 = 16.86.\n
Step 4: Round result to 1 decimal: 16.9.\n
Step 5: Bound of absolute error: h = 0.05 + 0.005 = 0.055.</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExQuestion_2">What is the bound of absolute error when adding values with h_a = 0.05 and h_b = 0.005?</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExAnswerOne_2">0.005</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExAnswerTwo_2">0.05</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExAnswerThree_2">0.055</string>
    <string name="SectionFourTheoryWorkedExCorrectAnswer_2">0.055</string>

